public class SuggestBox
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.SuggestBox
implements HasId, HasResponsiveness, HasPlaceholder, HasAutoComplete, HasSize<InputSize>, com.google.gwt.editor.client.HasEditorErrors<String>, HasErrorHandler, HasValidators<String>, HasBlankValidator<String>

Wrapper for a SuggestBox.

The default style is inherited from the Styles.DROPDOWN_MENU. Styling of the suggestions items need a bit of css in order to be pleasing to the eye. 

  .dropdown-menu .item {
      padding: 5px;
  }
  
  .dropdown-menu .item-selected {
      background-color: #eee;
  }

Author:
Steven Jardine
